{"tid":1390814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都覺得好無力 好羞恥","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:25:21.000Z","uid":167955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"89f9767d5658e77e9a4f4118a1d3023e29a90e1a","tid":1390814,"uid":167955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:45:40.000Z","msg":"眼見好多post都講話想派飯卷/資助，<br />\n但係平時自己真係除咗問人借一百幾十，又真係幾何問人拎過錢。<br />\n<br />\n但係我睇住自己8個隊友經濟又唔係好，<br />\n情況最差嗰個戶口得兩舊水，覺得自己真係好撚廢。<br />\n<br />\n自己不單止冇錢幫佢哋，仲要明知有幾個師兄係有心，都唔夠膽開口問。<br />\n搵個真係熟啲嘅friend資助一千蚊，都已經覺得羞恥到仆街 <br />\n<br />\n有冇前線巴打絲打都有同感 真係唔知自己應該要點開口問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1b98df9e3d4ac72096e1cdeceb6373f30ba4cd","tid":1390814,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkT1vED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkT1vED.png&h=0accd33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad74cdea241c203007599b18540dff5ad10e4e52","tid":1390814,"uid":212441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"一齊渡過呢個難關，好多人想幫你，唔洗猶豫"},{"pid":"9cf30396525b0c5897e52d2668da814ecef2ab25","tid":1390814,"uid":167955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad74cdea241c203007599b18540dff5ad10e4e52","tid":13